This fails with JSON.NET on webassembly but that's not Blazor's problem. I'm trying to do a similar thing with JsonUtil / SimpleJson and it sort of works but arrays come back null. so the following json:

```
{"array1":[{"key1":"value1"},{"key1":"value2"}]}
```

`JsonUtil.Deserialize(...json from above...)`

